onvert - $997)** - Wireframe layout - Section breakdown table - Discount messaging analysis - Form field specifications **PAGE 3: Tier 2 PIF Checkout (Built To Convert Plus - $2997)** - Wireframe layout - Section breakdown table - Value stack comparison - Upsell positioning **PAGE 4: Tier 2 Monthly Checkout ($579/month)** - Wireframe layout - Payment plan psychology - Affordability messaging **PAGE 5: Tier 2 12-Pay Checkout ($297/month)** - Wireframe layout - Low barrier entry positioning **PAGE 6: Tier 1 Monthly Checkout ($147/month)** - Wireframe layout - Entry-level positioning 5. **Copywriting Framework Table** - Create detailed table with columns: Copy Element | Headline Formula | Subheadline Pattern | Body Copy Structure | CTA Language | Objection Handled - Include rows for: Discount announcements, Bonus sections, FAQ answers, Testimonials, Scarcity/Urgency, Risk reversal 6. **Design Specification System** - Typography hierarchy table (H1, H2, H3, Body, CTA button text) - Color psychology breakdown table - Button design specifications - Image/media placement rules - White space and rhythm guidelines 7. **Conversion Mechanism Checklist** - Create checklist table for each page type - Include: Urgency elements, Social proof placements, Value stack, Risk reversal, Objection handling, Multiple CTAs, Trust badges 8. **AI Agent Replication Protocol** - Step-by-step SOP table with columns: Step # | Action Required | Input Data Needed | Expected Output | Quality Check - Include steps for: Brand color extraction, Font identification, Copy pattern analysis, Section replication, CRO element placement, Testing protocol 9. **Niche Adaptation Framework** - Table showing how to adapt each element for different industries - Columns: Original Element | Fitness Niche | Business Coaching | E-commerce | SaaS | Course Creation - Variable elements: Headlines, Testimonials, Bonus types, Urgency triggers, Price points 10. **Implementation SOP Table** - Detailed tactical steps with columns: Phase | Task | Tools Needed | Time Estimate | Success Metric | Common Pitfalls - Phases: Research, Design setup, Content creation, CRO implementation, Testing, Launch Use professional business formatting with clear headings, detailed tables, and structured sections. Include placeholder brackets like [YOUR BRAND COLOR] and [YOUR PRODUCT NAME] throughout for easy customization. Make all tables comprehensive with specific, actionable details. Perfect! Now let me create additional interactive visualizations and expand the document with detailed wireframes and the AI agent replication system. Using Tool | Doc View Viewing document: 1,100 Now let me add interactive flowcharts and detailed wireframe visualizations to enhance the document: Using Tool | Doc Edit --- a/document.html+++ b/document.html@@ -121,9 +121,21 @@   </head> <body> <h1>High-Converting 2-Tier Sales Funnel Template System</h1> -    <p><strong>Date:</strong> October 2023</p> +    <p><strong>Date:</strong> December 2025</p> <p><strong>Version:</strong> 1.0</p> <p><strong>Status:</strong> Approved for Replication</p> +    <p><strong>Source Analysis:</strong> Brandon Lucero Bots2Convert & Built To Convert Funnel</p> + +    <div style=\"background: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 16px; margin: 20px 0;\"> +      <h4 style=\"margin-top: 0; color: #856404;\">🎯 What This Template Delivers</h4> +      <ul style=\"margin-bottom: 0;\"> +        <li>Complete UI/UX wireframes for all 6 funnel pages</li> +        <li>Exact CRO conversion mechanisms for each section</li> +        <li>Copywriting frameworks with plug-and-play formulas</li> +        <li>AI Agent replication protocol for any niche</li> +        <li>Step-by-step tactical SOP with expected inputs/outputs</li> +      </ul> +    </div> <h2>1. Executive Summary</h2> <p> Now let me view and enhance the wireframe sections with more detailed visual representations: Using Tool | Doc View Viewing document: 250,350 Let me continue viewing and t