rm positioning Bonus stack arrangement Social proof grid Form field sequences 5. Copywriting Framework Plug-and-play formulas for: Headlines: \"[Action Verb] + [Benefit] + [Without Pain Point]\" FAQs: \"Do I need this if [Common Objection]?\" Testimonials: \"[Name] + [Emotional Quote] + [Specific Metric]\" CTAs: Context-appropriate button copy Urgency: \"Must enroll by [Time/Date]\" 6. Design Specification System Typography hierarchy (H1, H2, H3, Body, CTA) Color psychology breakdown Button design specs (dimensions, shadows, hover states) White space and rhythm guidelines Brand consistency rules 7. CRO Conversion Mechanism Checklist For each page type, includes: Urgency element placement Social proof positioning (every 800-1200px scroll) Value stack presentation Risk reversal techniques Objection handling locations Multiple CTA strategy 8. AI Agent Replication Protocol (The Game-Changer!) Phase 1: Brand DNA Extraction Color extraction with hex codes Typography identification Spacing documentation Button specifications Phase 2: Copywriting Pattern Analysis Headline formula extraction FAQ question patterns Testimonial structure templates Urgency language mapping CTA button copy formulas Phase 3: CRO Element Mapping Discount badge placement rules Price anchoring techniques Social proof rhythm Bonus stack hierarchy Form field optimization Phase 4: AI Agent Training Instructions Complete prompt template including: Required inputs (7 data points) Expected outputs (5 deliverables) Conversion rules (8 non-negotiables) Embedded psychology principles Phase 5: Niche Adaptation Framework Custom adaptations for 5 industries: Fitness/Health Business/Marketing Course Creation E-commerce SaaS/Tech Phase 6: Implementation Checklist Step-by-step SOP with: Task descriptions Tools needed Input required (as you requested!) Expected output (as you requested!) Success metrics Time estimates Phase 7: Quality Assurance Protocol 6-point QA checklist with pass/fail criteria 9. Niche Adaptation Framework Ready-to-use variations showing how to adapt: Headlines for different industries Social proof types Urgency mechanisms Testimonial formats Price point positioning 10. Implementation SOP Tactical 5-phase deployment plan: Research (2 days) Design Setup (3 days) Content Creation (4 days) Tech Integration (2 days) Launch & Optimization (ongoing) Each phase includes common pitfalls to avoid! 🔥 Key Features You Asked For: ✅ Detailed wireframes for every section of every page ✅ CRO conversion intent for each element documented ✅ Copywriting analysis with plug-and-play formulas ✅ AI Agent protocol that can replicate without error ✅ Step-by-step tactical SOP with click-by-click instructions ✅ Input/Output columns for every recommendation (as requested!) ✅ Expected results and quality checks for validation ✅ Niche adaptation - replicate for any industry in seconds 💡 How to Use This Template: For Manual Implementation: Use the wireframes and copywriting frameworks to build pages in your page builder (Kajabi, ClickFunnels, etc.) For AI Agent Creation: Copy the Core Agent Prompt Template (Section 12, Phase 4) into your AI system and feed it the required inputs For Client Work: Use the Niche Adaptation Framework to quickly customize for different industries For QA: Run through the Quality Assurance Protocol before launch 🚀 Next Steps: Would you like me to: Create interactive flowcharts showing the customer journey through the funnel? Generate specific copywriting examples for a particular niche? Build a simplified \"quick start\" checklist for rapid deployment? Create comparison charts showing conversion optimization for each element? Design the actual AI agent prompt as a standalone tool you can deploy? This template is production-ready and contains everything needed to replicate Brandon Lucero's funnel architecture at the same level of conversion specificity! 🎯 Brandon Lucero Sales Funnel Template & Knowledge Base Click to open Edit in AI Docs Now let me create inte