]}]}],\"title\":\"Brandon Lucero's 2-Tier Funnel Architecture\",\"width\":800,\"height\":500} View Now let me create a step-by-step implementation table as requested: 🚀 BRANDON LUCERO FUNNEL REPLICATION SYSTEM Based on my analysis of all 6 pages in Brandon's funnel, I've created a complete template system that you can use to replicate this high-converting architecture in any niche. Here's your comprehensive breakdown: 📊 FUNNEL FLOW VISUALIZATION This shows the complete customer journey through Brandon's 2-tier offer structure with multiple payment options. 💰 PRICING STRATEGY ANALYSIS Notice how Brandon strategically prices the payment plans HIGHER than PIF to incentivize immediate purchase while still offering flexibility. 🎯 FUNNEL ARCHITECTURE BREAKDOWN The treemap shows how Brandon allocates funnel real estate - 45% for Tier 2 (higher value), 35% for Tier 1, and 20% for entry. 📱 CHECKOUT PAGE WIREFRAME TEMPLATE This wireframe shows the exact layout structure used across all checkout pages in the funnel. 📋 DETAILED IMPLEMENTATION SOP TABLE Phase\tTask Description\tRequired Input\tExpected Output\tTools Needed\tSuccess Metrics\tTime Est. 1. Research & Analysis\tAnalyze competitor funnels and identify niche-specific pain points\tTarget niche, competitor URLs, ideal customer avatar\tCompetitive analysis report, pain point matrix, messaging angles\tWeb scraper, analysis tools\t5+ pain points identified, 3+ messaging angles\t2 days 2. Offer Structure Setup\tDefine your 2-tier offer structure with payment options\tProduct/service details, pricing strategy, value stack components\tTier 1 & Tier 2 offer definitions, payment plan matrix\tSpreadsheet, calculator\tClear value differentiation, profitable payment plans\t1 day 3. Copy Framework Development\tCreate headlines, subheads, FAQs, and testimonials using Brandon's formulas\tNiche research, customer testimonials, objection list\tComplete copy document with all page variants\tDoc editor, copy templates\tConversion-focused copy for all 6 pages\t3 days 4. Design System Creation\tEstablish visual hierarchy, colors, and conversion elements\tBrand colors, logo, image assets\tDesign system guide, UI component library\tDesign tools (Canva/Figma)\tConsistent visual brand across funnel\t2 days 5. Landing Page Build\tConstruct main sales/landing page with FAQ and testimonials\tFinalized copy, design assets, hosting platform\tLive landing page with conversion tracking\tPage builder (Kajabi/ClickFunnels)\tPage loads under 3 seconds, mobile responsive\t1 day 6. Checkout Pages Setup\tBuild all 6 checkout variants with order forms\tPayment processor setup, product configurations\t6 functional checkout pages with payment integration\tPage builder + payment gateway\tAll payment flows tested and working\t2 days 7. Conversion Optimization\tAdd urgency timers, social proof, and CRO elements\tSocial proof assets, urgency copy, trust badges\tFully optimized pages with conversion mechanisms\tCRO tools, timer scripts\tAll conversion elements properly placed\t1 day 8. Testing & QA\tTest all funnel paths, forms, and payment processing\tTest credit cards, various devices/browsers\tQA report with all issues resolved\tTesting tools, multiple devices\t100% funnel completion rate in tests\t1 day 🎯 CONVERSION ELEMENT SPECIFICATIONS Hero Section CRO Elements: Discount Badge: 44% off positioned top-right, creates immediate value perception Headline Formula: \"SAVE [%] NOW!\" + Product benefit statement Order Form Placement: Above the fold, reduces friction to purchase Social Proof Strategy: Testimonial Rhythm: Every 800-1200px of scroll Format: Name + Emotional quote + Specific metric (e.g., \"$20k in 3 weeks\") Positioning: Between bonus sections to maintain engagement Urgency Mechanisms: Time Sensitivity: \"Must enroll by [specific time/date]\" Scarcity Language: \"Only for students who enroll by 5pm PST TODAY\" Bonus Stack: Time-limited workshops and events Payment Psychology: Price Anchoring: Show crossed-out \"normal\" price vs. discounted price Payment Plan Premium: Monthly plans cost MORE than PIF to incentivize immediate payment Multiple Options: 3-5 payment choices to match different buyer preferences 🤖 AI AGENT REPLICATION SYSTEM I've created a complete AI agent system in your knowledge base document that includes: ✅ Complete Page Templates for all 6 funnel pages ✅ Copywriting Formulas that plug into any niche ✅ Design Specifications for brand consistency ✅ CRO Element Checklists for each page type ✅ Niche Adaptation Framework for 5+ industries 📖 Access Your Complete Knowledge Base: VIEW FULL TEMPLATE SYSTEM This includes: Detailed wireframes for every page section Complete copywriting framework with fill-in-the-blank templates CRO conversion intent analysis for each element AI agent prompt templates for automated replication Step-by-step implementation SOPs with input/output specifications 🚀 NEXT STEPS TO IMPLEMENT: Choose Your Niche - Use the adaptation framework in the knowledge base Set Up Your Offers - Follow the 2-tier structure template Deploy the AI Agent - Use the provided prompts to automate page creation Test & Optimize - Follow the QA checklist before launch Would you like me to: Create specific copy examples for your niche? Build the actual AI agent as a standalone tool? Design additional conversion elements or A/B test variations? Generate specific wireframes for your industry? This system gives you everything needed to replicate Brandon's funnel at the exact same level of conversion specificity! 🎯 Build the actual a I agent as a standalone tool and design.Additional conversion elements or a b test variations I'll create a standalone AI agent tool and design additional conversion elements with A/B test variations for you. Let me build this comprehensive system. Agent at Work | AI Developer Brandon Lucero Funnel Replicator AI Agent View I'll build a comprehensive AI Agent tool as a standalone web application that can replicate Brandon Lucero's sales funn